[We have gone over this many times. As Drs. Wilde and Morley have stated,
the vaccine has been shown to be safe and effective. If it is not being
employed where it should be, that is a question of judgement (poor), will
(insufficient), money (insufficient), knowledge (insufficient) or all four.
JE, yellow fever, measles, mumps, rubella, polio, and other diseases are
preventable. If they are not prevented that is another story altogether.
